sections.heading: IV-D Support Payment Distributive Fund; created; use
sections.text: The Title IV-D Support Payment Distributive Fund is created. The fund shall be used for the collection and disbursement of support payments as provided in sections 43-3341 to 43-3347.SourceLaws 1999, LB 637, ยง 6;Laws 2000, LB 972, ยง 31;Laws 2004,
